  "title": "COMMIS CHEF",
  "description": "<p>Position: Commis Chef 1</p><p><br /></p><p>Monthly Salary: $3,200.00 (negotiable)</p><p><br /></p><p>We are launching a vibrant new bar-restaurant in one of Singapore's busiest districts and are looking for passionate Commis Chefs to join our team. This is a great opportunity to gain hands-on experience in food preparation, cooking, and kitchen hygiene, while growing your career ina fast-paced and suppportive environment. If you are detailed-oriented, team-driven, and ready to be part of something exciting, we would love to hear from you!</p><p><br /></p><p>Job Responsibilities:</p><p>- Assist in the preparation and cooking of ramen and other Japanese dishes according to standard recipes</p><p>- Maintain high standards of food hygiene and kitchen cleanliness</p><p>- Support senior chefs in daily kitchen operations</p><p>- Ensure food preparation areas and equipment are properly cleaned and maintained</p><p>- Assist in stock checks, receiving deliveries, and proper storage of ingrdients</p><p>- Adhere to safety and sanitation guidelines at all times</p><p>- Perform other kitchen duties as assigned</p><p><br /></p><p>Requirement:</p><p>- 3 years of relevant culinary experience (training will be provided)</p><p>- Strong interest in culinary and willingness to learn</p><p>- Team player with a positive and respectful attitude</p><p>- Good communication and time management skills</p><p>- Able to work in a high-pressure kichen environment</p><p>- Must be available on weekends and public holidays</p><p>- WSQ Certificate (Food Hygiene Certificate)</p><p><br /></p><p>What we offer:</p><p>- 5-day work week</p><p>- Alternate split & straight shft schedule</p><p>- Staff meals and uniforms provided</p><p>- Medical benefits</p><p>- Employee discounts</p><p>- A supportive and collaborative kitchen environment</p><p>- Opportunities for skill development and career growth</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p>",
